      "role": "user",
      "content": "the \"what's next\" part is what's hard. it feels less like a new chapter and more like i've just run out of road. like the journey is done and there's nothing left behind the horizon but a void. it’s almost peaceful, thinking about just... stopping. not seeing another sunrise, not booking another flight. just staying right here.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
